text: Beechwood is a private housing estate in Runcorn, Cheshire. It has two primary schools (Hillview and Beechwood Primary), a community centre, a pub, a church, and a local shop. The Beechwood estate was developed during the mid to late 1970s by an American owned company named "Whelmar" ==External links== Category: Runcorn
